                p No convoluted spreadsheets or legacy software. 42 makes data&nbsp;intuitive.

            article.key-content
                p.icon.customicon-home-point-2
                h2 Reduce Cost, Grow&nbsp;Revenue
                p Access your data from the cloud. No hardware, no downloads, no&nbsp;fuss.

            article.key-content
                p.icon.customicon-home-point-3
                h2 Monetize Your POS&nbsp;Data
                p Instantly share your findings with clients and colleagues. Export PDFs and&nbsp;graphs.


    section.how.feature

        .wrapper

            article.hero-content
                h2 How It Works

                ul
                    li
                        i.step
                        p We take raw data and process it on our web&nbsp;platform.

                    li
                        i.step
                        p Our algorithms scan the data to find the best ways to grow your business. 42's technology can identify opportunity areas to increase growth and reduce inefficiencies.

                    li
                        i.step
                        p Get recommendations for where to focus your resources next.

                    li
                        a.outline-btn(ui-sref="root.demo.signup") Try Our Demo

                img.how-it-works(src="/assets/images/how.svg")


    section.testimonials

        .wrapper(ng-mouseenter="carousel.stop()", ng-mouseleave="carousel.start()")
            .quote-wrapper
                q(ng-bind-html="testimonials[carousel.state.index].quote")

            ul.people
                li(ng-repeat="testimonial in testimonials"
                  ,ng-class="{active:carousel.state.index == $index}"
                  ,ng-mouseover="select($index)")

                    img(ng-src="{{ testimonial.image }}")

                    div
                        h4(ng-bind-html="testimonial.name")
                        h3(ng-bind-html="testimonial.title")


